-- KKR Mulls Buyout of Italian Diagnostics Company Diasorin, Il Mondo Reports
-- Marco Bertacche
-- 2010-08-06T06:48:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/kkr-mulls-buyout-of-italy-diagnostic-test-supplier-diasorin-il-mondo-says.html

          
          
             KKR & Co. is considering a buyout of
Diasorin SpA, an Italian supplier of diagnostic tests, weekly
magazine Il Mondo reported without saying how it obtained the
information.  
 The buyout is likely to involve Chief Executive Officer
Carlo Rosa, the magazine said, without elaborating.  
          
          


  


        